## What If I Already Have an SEO Strategy?

If your current strategy is producing results — consistent ranking growth, increasing organic leads, compounding traffic — keep it. If it isn't, the problem is almost certainly in the architecture rather than the execution.

The most common strategy failures I diagnose for Reading businesses: content production without topical map architecture (content that doesn't reinforce itself), technical roadmaps built on automated reports without human interpretation (long lists of issues with no clear priority), and keyword targeting without entity alignment (chasing individual terms instead of building comprehensive expertise signals).

A strategy review — rather than a full strategy build — may be sufficient if foundations are in place. Focused strategy sessions start from £200 and deliver prioritised recommendations your team can implement immediately.

